Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/michal-au/.vim.git ~/.vim

Create symlink:

    ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/.tmux.conf ~/.tmux.conf
    ln -s ~/.vim/.inputrc ~/.inputrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
